div.p:
Rec. Olei rosarum ℥.ix. or els halfe so much;
   Apollonius
 put it into a leaden morter with a péece of leade; labour it therewith vntill it become thicke and blacke like vnto leade, then beate seuerallie Litharge and white leade, of each lib.j. or lib.ss. Mingle them with the oyle and frame your Liniment.
